<!-- AQUATIC THERAPY -->
<section class="section section--cream">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="intro-split">
      <div class="intro-split__body reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Aquatic Therapy</span>
        <h2>The most effective workout most people have never tried.</h2>
        <p class="lead">Our indoor, heated saltwater pool is one of the few amenities of its kind at a senior living community in Fayette County, and it&rsquo;s central to everything we do in wellness.</p>
        <p>Water provides 12 times the resistance of air on the body while making you feel approximately 90% lighter. The result is a cardiovascular workout with minimal joint stress. That&rsquo;s exactly what seniors need, and the elimination of fear of falling in warm, supportive water is itself therapeutic for many residents.</p>
        <p>Aquatic programs run individually and in groups and are ideal for residents managing:</p>
        <ul class="tag-list">
          <li>Balance issues and fall risk</li>
          <li>Arthritis and joint conditions</li>
          <li>Back, foot, and leg injuries</li>
          <li>Knee conditions</li>
          <li>Cardiac recovery</li>
          <li>Post-surgical rehabilitation</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="intro-split__media reveal">
        <img src="{{ images.wellnessPool }}" alt="Water aerobics class in our heated indoor saltwater pool" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

